WEBVTT

01:30.900 --> 01:34.990
[Dream of Golden Years]

01:35.150 --> 01:35.920
Open your eyes wide

01:35.789 --> 01:39.440
[2024]

01:35.920 --> 01:37.180
and look for yourself—

01:37.229 --> 01:38.690
where do you think you are?

01:38.870 --> 01:40.000
This is Shengcheng!

01:40.509 --> 01:41.710
Top university grads,

01:41.710 --> 01:43.039
those who studied abroad—

01:43.039 --> 01:44.509
every single one of them
swallows their pride

01:44.509 --> 01:45.910
and works like a dog here!

01:46.430 --> 01:47.229
I'm telling you,

01:47.229 --> 01:48.640
if you still want to keep your job,

01:48.640 --> 01:49.840
swallow

01:50.039 --> 01:50.950
whatever you shouldn't have said

01:50.950 --> 01:52.150
and keep your mouth shut!

01:52.150 --> 01:52.789
Mr. Wang,

01:53.150 --> 01:54.120
there's a detail in the contract

01:54.120 --> 01:55.979
I'd like to go over with you again!

02:01.510 --> 02:02.760
Thank you, Ms. Xia.

02:03.680 --> 02:05.340
It's okay. Don't be too upset.

02:14.240 --> 02:15.430
Since when did you start liking

02:15.430 --> 02:17.280
meddling in other people's business?

02:17.280 --> 02:19.210
Just what's left of my conscience.

02:20.190 --> 02:23.250
Be careful, or your conscience
will get you in trouble.

02:27.220 --> 02:29.900
[Episode 35: Do You Dare Face Yourself?]

02:31.579 --> 02:35.690
[Kong Island]

02:32.110 --> 02:33.640
Still nothing newsworthy.

02:34.030 --> 02:36.030
Yeah, total waste of film.

02:36.800 --> 02:38.800
Do you think Mr. Du will ever wake up?

02:39.470 --> 02:41.030
He's been in a coma for so long.

02:41.030 --> 02:42.690
If he wakes up, I'll eat my hat.

02:42.770 --> 02:45.079
You think we've been waiting here
all this time

02:45.079 --> 02:46.340
just for him to wake up?

02:46.680 --> 02:48.079
After waiting this long,

02:48.120 --> 02:50.240
of course, we're here
to grab the first scoop.

02:50.240 --> 02:52.840
Exactly, now that's something
worth hearing.

02:57.590 --> 02:58.079
Dad.

03:00.240 --> 03:00.800
Dad!

03:02.560 --> 03:04.220
Haven't visited in a few days.

03:04.360 --> 03:05.710
Did you miss me?

03:07.590 --> 03:08.960
Probably not.

03:09.470 --> 03:10.590
Anyway, every day,

03:10.910 --> 03:13.040
you have Vivi putting on a show for you.

03:18.030 --> 03:19.230
And speaking of that,

03:19.800 --> 03:21.260
you should be thanking me.

03:21.590 --> 03:23.079
I paid for Vivi's

03:23.310 --> 03:25.240
face and body—the whole makeover.

03:27.120 --> 03:27.630
You should've seen

03:27.630 --> 03:29.230
what she looked like before.

03:30.079 --> 03:30.840
So tacky.

03:37.960 --> 03:39.550
Just stay in your coma!

03:39.710 --> 03:41.400
I've sold the whole shipping business!

03:41.400 --> 03:42.470
I'll sell the entire

03:42.470 --> 03:43.240
Chengrong Group too!

03:43.240 --> 03:44.190
Do you believe me?

03:44.190 --> 03:45.030
Do you?

03:54.800 --> 03:56.590
You're really not going to wake up?

03:56.590 --> 03:57.590
That won't do.

03:58.520 --> 03:59.190
Then how will you see

03:59.190 --> 04:00.590
how capable I've become?

04:01.560 --> 04:02.470
How will you feel

04:02.470 --> 04:04.470
what it's like to be abandoned
by everyone?

04:04.470 --> 04:05.670
If you stay like this,

04:05.750 --> 04:07.680
how am I supposed to get my revenge?

04:28.720 --> 04:29.920
Take good care of him.

04:30.560 --> 04:31.800
Anything unusual lately?

04:31.800 --> 04:32.310
Ms. Vivi

04:32.310 --> 04:34.040
comes to visit Mr. Du every day.

04:34.680 --> 04:36.210
Let her come if she wants to.

04:36.480 --> 04:37.000
If she actually

04:37.000 --> 04:38.130
wakes the old man up,

04:39.120 --> 04:40.980
I'll have to give her a big reward.

04:43.720 --> 04:44.740
Ms. Vivi,

04:44.800 --> 04:45.270
you're truly devoted

04:45.270 --> 04:46.390
to the old man.

04:47.560 --> 04:48.760
If he really wakes up,

04:48.930 --> 04:50.860
he'll definitely reward you well.

04:51.360 --> 04:52.680
I'm going in to check on the Master.

04:52.680 --> 04:54.010
I should be thanking you

04:54.270 --> 04:56.930
for giving me the chance
to play the dutiful son.

04:59.040 --> 05:00.430
I'm going in to check on the Master.

05:00.430 --> 05:01.690
No one is stopping you.

05:07.390 --> 05:08.110
Shit! Shit!

05:08.110 --> 05:09.240
Shit! Young Master!

05:09.360 --> 05:11.760
Mrs. Du is on the roof,
threatening to jump!

05:11.860 --> 05:12.830
Why are you just standing there?

05:12.830 --> 05:13.960
Come with me, quick!

05:14.000 --> 05:14.430
Yes.

05:15.240 --> 05:15.870
Calm down! Calm down!

05:15.870 --> 05:17.120
Don't come any closer!

05:17.120 --> 05:17.800
Step back!

05:18.310 --> 05:19.310
Step back!

05:19.390 --> 05:20.310
-Calm down!
-Calm down!

05:20.310 --> 05:20.920
You too!

05:21.430 --> 05:23.390
Back off! Step back!

05:23.510 --> 05:24.510
I'm going to jump!

05:29.070 --> 05:30.600
Out of the way! Out of the way!

05:30.600 --> 05:33.870
Stop filming!
Go point that camera at your own wife!

05:34.240 --> 05:35.070
Du Zhaohui,

05:35.560 --> 05:37.560
you have the nerve to show your face?

05:38.310 --> 05:39.640
You harmed your own dad,

05:40.000 --> 05:40.920
framed Zhaoji,

05:41.390 --> 05:42.920
and colluded with Mr. Cheng

05:43.360 --> 05:44.159
to forge the power of attorney

05:44.159 --> 05:45.420
to take over the group!

05:45.510 --> 05:46.950
You wolf in sheep's clothing—

05:46.950 --> 05:49.550
you didn't even spare
your own flesh and blood!

05:49.630 --> 05:50.490
Mr. Du Zhaohui,

05:50.630 --> 05:51.680
is what Mrs. Du said true?

05:51.680 --> 05:52.630
Of course, it's true!

05:52.630 --> 05:54.190
Every word I say is true!

05:54.600 --> 05:55.720
You reporters,

05:55.750 --> 05:57.510
you just love the drama, don't you?

05:57.510 --> 05:58.670
Don't block the medical staff!

05:58.670 --> 05:59.720
Kick them all out!

06:00.040 --> 06:00.840
Kick them out!

06:01.160 --> 06:02.040
Don't go!

06:02.950 --> 06:04.120
He's lying!

06:04.120 --> 06:05.160
I'm telling the truth!

06:05.160 --> 06:06.070
Don't leave!

06:08.360 --> 06:09.090
Auntie Song,

06:09.480 --> 06:10.940
do you really want to jump?

06:11.600 --> 06:12.600
From this height,

06:12.720 --> 06:13.870
you probably won't die.

06:13.870 --> 06:15.390
It'll just hurt a lot.

06:21.270 --> 06:22.430
Stop agitating her!

06:22.720 --> 06:24.320
Don't come closer! Back off!

06:24.480 --> 06:25.360
Back off!

06:41.480 --> 06:42.830
They've forced me.

06:44.680 --> 06:45.680
Don't blame me.

06:47.920 --> 06:48.920
It'll be quick.

06:50.560 --> 06:52.020
You won't suffer for long.

06:54.720 --> 06:55.650
I'm actually...

06:57.120 --> 06:58.430
setting you free.

07:00.240 --> 07:02.380
If you had considered me a bit more,

07:02.920 --> 07:04.360
I wouldn't have been in

07:04.360 --> 07:06.420
such an embarrassing situation now.

07:07.870 --> 07:09.510
I tried so hard to please you,

07:11.240 --> 07:13.640
just to make sure
you can't live without me.

07:14.070 --> 07:15.000
But did you really think

07:15.000 --> 07:17.000
I like being with an old man like you?

07:18.160 --> 07:19.690
If it weren't for survival,

07:20.270 --> 07:21.600
who would do any of this?

07:23.240 --> 07:23.830
You said

07:23.830 --> 07:25.270
you'd give me a life of luxury.

07:25.270 --> 07:26.560
But what happened?

07:27.560 --> 07:29.310
You don't care about me at all.

08:37.080 --> 08:38.000
Old fool.

08:39.720 --> 08:40.960
You got to enjoy such a young

08:40.960 --> 08:42.320
and beautiful body.

08:43.630 --> 08:44.690
You came out ahead.

08:50.270 --> 08:52.000
What do you think you're doing?

08:57.870 --> 08:58.400
It's you!

08:58.630 --> 08:59.560
You want me dead!

08:59.870 --> 09:01.270
You want your own father dead

09:01.270 --> 09:02.320
and Zhaoji too!

09:02.440 --> 09:03.370
Young Master Du!

09:03.600 --> 09:05.000
Your father has woken up.

09:06.790 --> 09:07.790
Did you hear that?

09:07.910 --> 09:09.040
The old man is awake.

09:09.440 --> 09:10.270
Go ahead and jump.

09:10.270 --> 09:12.130
He can even arrange your funeral.

09:12.790 --> 09:14.060
Mrs. Du, stop messing around!

09:14.060 --> 09:15.990
You'll have to pay if you damage it!

09:18.600 --> 09:19.320
He's awake?

09:20.790 --> 09:21.920
How could he wake up?

09:22.840 --> 09:23.970
How could he wake up?

09:28.440 --> 09:29.570
What should I do now?

09:30.200 --> 09:31.330
What should I do now?

09:31.870 --> 09:32.720
What do I do?

09:34.000 --> 09:35.120
What do I do?

10:05.790 --> 10:06.910
Ms. Vivi,

10:07.480 --> 10:08.210
impressive.

10:09.000 --> 10:11.130
You even managed to wake the old man up.

10:12.150 --> 10:13.750
That's a great achievement.

10:15.030 --> 10:16.120
It's all because

10:16.870 --> 10:18.070
he's favored by fate.

10:22.600 --> 10:23.030
Young Master Du.

10:23.030 --> 10:24.030
Doctor, how is he?

10:24.150 --> 10:25.360
Your father's intracranial hemorrhage

10:25.360 --> 10:26.820
hasn't fully cleared yet.

10:26.840 --> 10:27.750
We still need to wait for

10:27.750 --> 10:30.070
the detailed examination report
for specifics.

10:30.070 --> 10:31.120
But the good news is,

10:31.120 --> 10:32.910
he has regained consciousness.

10:32.910 --> 10:33.970
Thank you, doctor.

10:34.030 --> 10:35.630
Your father wants to see you.

10:36.000 --> 10:37.550
He has something to tell you.

10:37.550 --> 10:37.900
Okay.

10:37.940 --> 10:38.870
Thank you, doctor.

10:38.870 --> 10:39.200
Okay.

10:40.630 --> 10:41.030
Hua.

10:41.720 --> 10:42.600
Lock down this entire floor.

10:42.600 --> 10:43.960
Don't let any reporters in,

10:43.960 --> 10:45.960
and don't let anyone out.

10:46.270 --> 10:46.910
Got it.

10:53.350 --> 10:54.060
Ms. Vivi.

10:55.080 --> 10:56.010
What do you want?

10:56.630 --> 10:57.030
I...

10:58.510 --> 10:59.910
You must want some water.

11:00.390 --> 11:01.920
Get some water for Ms. Vivi.

11:02.840 --> 11:05.040
You've had a long day. Sit down and rest.

11:06.270 --> 11:09.000
You also heard the young master—
no one's allowed to leave.

11:09.000 --> 11:11.000
Don't make things difficult for me.

11:26.960 --> 11:28.290
Hungry after waking up?

11:28.960 --> 11:30.090
Wanna a banana, Dad?

11:32.550 --> 11:34.010
Don't look at me like that.

11:34.030 --> 11:34.890
Let me tell you,

11:35.500 --> 11:36.320
I've already sold

11:36.320 --> 11:37.980
the entire shipping company.

11:38.240 --> 11:39.480
There was no stopping it.

11:39.480 --> 11:41.410
The contracts are already signed.

11:44.320 --> 11:45.850
Our family has come to this.

11:46.270 --> 11:47.000
Besides,

11:48.360 --> 11:49.490
why would I stop you?

11:53.150 --> 11:54.480
And as for the smuggling business,

11:54.480 --> 11:56.010
I've completely removed it

11:56.150 --> 11:57.520
from our family's operations.

11:57.520 --> 11:58.500
Does that hurt?

11:59.720 --> 12:00.870
But in the long run,

12:00.870 --> 12:01.960
it's good for

12:02.440 --> 12:03.640
our Chengrong Group.

12:04.600 --> 12:05.840
As for your Liu Keying,

12:05.840 --> 12:06.570
she ran away.

12:06.960 --> 12:07.600
Your wife

12:07.870 --> 12:08.800
is up on the roof,

12:08.910 --> 12:10.510
making a scene
in front of every media outlet,

12:10.510 --> 12:11.710
threatening to jump.

12:12.200 --> 12:13.460
Go up and talk her down?

12:15.390 --> 12:16.630
I'm not interested.

12:18.510 --> 12:19.360
Then what about your son?

12:19.360 --> 12:21.210
Do you care about Du Zhaoji?

12:24.630 --> 12:25.630
He's downstairs.

12:31.270 --> 12:32.070
Young Master.

12:33.000 --> 12:34.460
Du Chengrong has woken up.

12:40.150 --> 12:42.280
Since he's tough enough to survive...

12:44.030 --> 12:44.890
Start the boat!

12:45.320 --> 12:45.670
Yes!

12:58.030 --> 12:58.630
No way!

12:59.240 --> 13:00.200
You put so much effort

13:00.200 --> 13:01.750
into raising this son of yours.

13:01.750 --> 13:03.550
Don't you feel anything for him?

13:05.790 --> 13:08.630
That brat tried to kill his own dad.

13:09.430 --> 13:11.360
He must bear all the consequences.

13:15.510 --> 13:16.000
Yong!

13:23.150 --> 13:23.780
Yong!

13:26.030 --> 13:27.230
Get ready to head out!

13:27.320 --> 13:28.520
Where is the captain?

13:29.370 --> 13:30.300
What's going on?

13:31.910 --> 13:32.670
Yong!

13:33.360 --> 13:34.220
What happened?

13:35.000 --> 13:35.860
Start the boat!

13:36.390 --> 13:37.050
Don't move,

13:37.080 --> 13:37.540
police!

13:45.550 --> 13:45.880
Move!

13:47.440 --> 13:47.970
Hurry up!

13:49.120 --> 13:49.580
Move it!

13:52.630 --> 13:52.960
Move!

14:00.320 --> 14:00.720
Hurry!

14:00.870 --> 14:01.240
Move!

14:07.870 --> 14:08.320
Move!

14:22.570 --> 14:23.320
Second Young Master Du,

14:23.320 --> 14:24.850
what is the meaning of this?

14:25.480 --> 14:26.630
You had someone

14:26.630 --> 14:28.490
deliver this jade pot to my daddy?

14:30.000 --> 14:32.200
I don't know what you're talking about.

14:34.630 --> 14:35.480
Trying to lure

14:35.480 --> 14:36.360
Du Chengrong out like this

14:36.360 --> 14:37.200
won't work.

14:37.870 --> 14:39.000
Without an insider,

14:39.440 --> 14:40.630
do you think he'd be foolish enough

14:40.630 --> 14:42.560
to come out alone to trade with you,

14:43.080 --> 14:43.910
Xu Zhongyi?

14:49.720 --> 14:50.790
Second Young Master Du,

14:50.790 --> 14:52.390
I'm not quite following you.

14:57.390 --> 14:59.190
Since I even know your real name,

14:59.630 --> 15:01.630
naturally, I've also investigated

15:01.720 --> 15:03.120
what happened back then.

15:05.510 --> 15:06.770
Who would have thought

15:07.120 --> 15:08.080
that our family's

15:08.080 --> 15:08.880
first fortune

15:09.360 --> 15:10.320
was all thanks to antiques

15:10.320 --> 15:11.650
taken from your family?

15:13.720 --> 15:14.840
My daddy always claimed

15:14.840 --> 15:16.240
he started from scratch.

15:19.600 --> 15:21.330
Turns out he relied on robbery.

15:24.720 --> 15:25.630
After all these years,

15:25.630 --> 15:28.160
you still haven't succeeded in
your revenge.

15:28.380 --> 15:29.880
You should know how cunning

15:29.880 --> 15:30.950
that old fox is.

15:32.470 --> 15:34.440
You've endured for decades.

15:34.870 --> 15:36.440
Being impatient now

15:36.870 --> 15:39.270
will only expose
your true identity to him.

15:40.150 --> 15:41.960
What exactly do you want me to do?

15:46.840 --> 15:49.790
I need you... to do me a favor.

15:59.270 --> 15:59.840
Mr. Qiu,

16:00.030 --> 16:02.030
you still came out on a day like this?

16:02.120 --> 16:02.870
You don't have to

16:02.870 --> 16:04.720
push yourself this hard for business, eh?

16:04.720 --> 16:05.360
Come on...

16:14.630 --> 16:15.200
Daddy.

16:16.120 --> 16:16.750
Zhaoji.

16:18.080 --> 16:19.880
When did you make this decision?

16:21.390 --> 16:22.320
These people...

16:23.440 --> 16:25.640
Liu Keying gave them to you, didn't she?

16:28.170 --> 16:30.010
When did you two join forces?

16:33.270 --> 16:34.530
Why should we tell you?

16:39.910 --> 16:41.870
It started from the moment I realized

16:41.870 --> 16:43.360
you were going senile.

16:45.320 --> 16:47.320
You're already old,

16:47.960 --> 16:49.960
but you just refuse to give up power.

16:50.120 --> 16:51.320
You just wanted to buy more time

16:51.320 --> 16:52.510
for Zhaohui to grow,

16:52.510 --> 16:53.170
didn't you?

16:53.720 --> 16:55.910
Don't you know what kind of person he is?

16:55.910 --> 16:57.430
You actually want to put

16:57.450 --> 16:58.780
such an idiot in charge?

17:00.390 --> 17:02.120
I need to correct your mistake.

17:02.630 --> 17:03.150
Mr. Du,

17:04.550 --> 17:06.069
you promised to marry me.

17:07.440 --> 17:08.960
Why did you break your promise

17:08.960 --> 17:11.270
and make me the laughingstock
of the whole island?

17:11.270 --> 17:12.730
My brother, Liu Tianquan,

17:12.920 --> 17:14.920
worked like a slave for your family.

17:15.790 --> 17:16.920
Now that you're old

17:17.510 --> 17:19.829
and want to clear obstacles
for your first son,

17:19.829 --> 17:21.880
you just kick us siblings aside.

17:23.160 --> 17:24.349
I begged you

17:24.349 --> 17:25.880
to spare my brother's life.

17:27.420 --> 17:28.880
What did you promise me?

17:39.240 --> 17:40.030
Liu Keying.

17:42.200 --> 17:43.960
How can you be this stupid?

17:44.200 --> 17:45.970
You've been by my side for over 10 years,

17:45.970 --> 17:47.840
yet you haven't learned from me

17:47.920 --> 17:50.000
that you can't just trust

17:50.110 --> 17:51.640
anyone around you!

17:52.720 --> 17:53.580
Think about it.

17:54.640 --> 17:56.480
He's not even 23 yet,

17:57.110 --> 17:59.790
and he dares to treat his dad like this—

17:59.920 --> 18:01.270
his own dad.

18:01.750 --> 18:03.160
Even if you have something on him,

18:03.160 --> 18:03.880
so what?

18:04.510 --> 18:06.840
You think that'll keep him under control?

18:10.200 --> 18:12.060
Looks like my choice was correct.

18:13.110 --> 18:15.510
Although Zhaohui can be reckless at times,

18:15.830 --> 18:19.790
he knows what he should

18:20.000 --> 18:21.920
and shouldn't do.

18:22.750 --> 18:23.510
But you—

18:24.640 --> 18:26.030
you're too greedy.

18:38.350 --> 18:40.830
A man who built his fortune
through robbery

18:41.830 --> 18:43.030
is calling me greedy?

18:45.270 --> 18:45.920
Daddy...

18:46.270 --> 18:47.680
Stop wasting words on him!

18:47.680 --> 18:48.310
Do it!

18:56.070 --> 18:57.130
At a time like this,

18:57.440 --> 18:59.570
don't you know who to point the guns at?

19:14.830 --> 19:16.160
You two scumbags,

19:16.160 --> 19:18.020
how dare you point your guns at me?

19:19.750 --> 19:21.030
What's wrong

19:21.030 --> 19:22.490
with pointing guns at you?

19:26.780 --> 19:27.510
Mr. Qiu.

19:29.550 --> 19:30.750
My surname isn't Qiu.

19:31.590 --> 19:34.310
My real name is Xu Zhongyi.

19:37.480 --> 19:38.790
Zhongyi, it's me.

19:39.390 --> 19:40.390
The boat is ready.

19:40.400 --> 19:41.530
You can leave today.

19:45.640 --> 19:47.790
Chengrong, the rain is so heavy outside.

19:47.790 --> 19:48.720
Is the boat safe?

19:53.310 --> 19:54.110
Du Chengrong,

19:54.320 --> 19:55.030
I've waited for this day

19:55.030 --> 19:56.110
for 30 years.

19:56.530 --> 19:57.180
Back then,

19:57.720 --> 19:58.920
you stole my antiques

19:59.240 --> 20:00.840
and killed my wife and child.

20:01.350 --> 20:04.110
You never expected
I'd live to see this day, did you?

20:04.110 --> 20:05.920
Today, I'm here to settle the score

20:05.920 --> 20:07.720
and take back what belongs to me.

20:08.920 --> 20:09.720
Du Chengrong,

20:10.200 --> 20:11.680
today is the day you die.

20:14.260 --> 20:15.510
Wait, let me gather my thoughts.

20:15.510 --> 20:16.230
I can't quite remember.

20:16.230 --> 20:17.110
You are...

20:20.160 --> 20:21.020
I remember now.

20:22.030 --> 20:23.240
Yes, I remember you!

20:24.310 --> 20:26.310
But today should not be the day I die.

20:43.880 --> 20:45.080
You've been managing

20:45.270 --> 20:47.270
the company for the past two months.

20:47.640 --> 20:48.790
Since you have the ability

20:48.790 --> 20:50.200
to keep it from going bankrupt

20:50.200 --> 20:51.680
even during a stock market crash,

20:51.680 --> 20:52.960
keep managing it.

20:55.240 --> 20:57.370
You can announce to the public that...

20:58.590 --> 21:00.320
I've regained consciousness.

21:01.440 --> 21:02.000
Also,

21:02.960 --> 21:04.200
let Vivi stay.

21:04.870 --> 21:05.680
You can go now.

21:06.640 --> 21:07.880
You don't need to keep working so hard

21:07.880 --> 21:09.350
pretending to be the dutiful son here.

21:09.350 --> 21:10.890
You're still thinking about Vivi?

21:10.890 --> 21:11.640
Let me tell you...

21:11.640 --> 21:12.830
Don't think

21:12.850 --> 21:14.160
I'm unaware
of what's been going on in the family.

21:14.160 --> 21:15.440
Nothing gets past me!

21:22.170 --> 21:22.930
Anyway,

21:23.480 --> 21:25.560
those people
who tried to kill you at the dock

21:25.560 --> 21:26.840
weren't sent by me.

21:29.640 --> 21:31.370
They wanted to keep smuggling.

21:31.480 --> 21:32.690
I couldn't stop them.

21:33.280 --> 21:34.680
But I won't do it anymore.

21:49.120 --> 21:49.820
That's all.

21:50.490 --> 21:51.170
Xia Ziyu

21:51.200 --> 21:52.720
probably won't have it easy.

21:52.720 --> 21:54.390
If you insist on
bringing her back to Shengcheng,

21:54.390 --> 21:55.350
I don't think the old man

21:55.350 --> 21:56.400
will stop you.

21:56.750 --> 21:58.000
He might even help you.

21:58.000 --> 21:59.600
Then I'll thank him for that.

22:00.480 --> 22:02.740
But the matter between Xia Ziyu and me...

22:02.960 --> 22:04.290
I must settle it myself.

22:09.750 --> 22:10.510
Xu Zhongyi

22:10.880 --> 22:12.350
might not be able to
come back for a while.

22:12.350 --> 22:13.110
That's still better than

22:13.110 --> 22:14.170
never coming back.

22:22.680 --> 22:23.330
Thank you.

22:33.110 --> 22:33.510
Here.

22:35.000 --> 22:35.750
Be careful.

22:35.800 --> 22:38.640
♪ Drifting with the wind and waves ♪

22:39.600 --> 22:42.440
♪ Drifting with the waves of life ♪

22:43.800 --> 22:46.990
♪ The moment our paths crossed ♪

22:47.740 --> 22:50.860
♪ We were instantly worlds apart ♪

22:51.800 --> 22:54.680
♪ Fate drifts with the wind ♪

22:52.480 --> 22:53.070
Xiaolan.

22:53.750 --> 22:54.680
Why are you here?

22:55.740 --> 22:58.700
♪ Watching over you even if fate ends ♪

22:55.790 --> 22:56.550
Wait here a moment.

22:56.550 --> 22:57.070
I'll go get the car.

22:57.070 --> 22:57.440
Okay.

22:57.720 --> 22:58.830
He'll bring the car here,

22:58.830 --> 22:59.680
then we'll go out.

22:59.650 --> 23:03.250
♪ The moment we gazed at each other ♪

22:59.680 --> 23:00.720
I'll be right back.

23:00.720 --> 23:01.510
It's windy outside.

23:01.510 --> 23:02.970
Let's wait inside for now.

23:03.590 --> 23:07.120
♪ Tears fell in my heart ♪

23:03.680 --> 23:05.440
Let me fix your scarf.

23:06.160 --> 23:06.760
It's fine.

23:07.110 --> 23:07.640
Let's go.

23:07.710 --> 23:08.420
-Let's go.
-Okay.

23:07.930 --> 23:11.390
♪ Even as we part,
I give you all my heart ♪

23:11.450 --> 23:15.040
♪ Silently enduring the twists of fate ♪

23:15.840 --> 23:19.810
♪ Someday, perhaps,
we'll be together again ♪

23:19.840 --> 23:22.590
♪ Reliving the past ♪

23:23.850 --> 23:31.260
♪ And yet, we may never meet again ♪

23:31.860 --> 23:38.130
♪ The twilight sky in that distant land
feels even farther away ♪

23:39.740 --> 23:42.800
♪ Who stands on the golden shore? ♪

23:43.890 --> 23:47.050
♪ Who waits beyond the smoke of war? ♪

23:47.930 --> 23:51.300
♪ In that fleeting glance back ♪

23:51.910 --> 23:55.190
♪ We softly ask how we've fared ♪

24:10.550 --> 24:12.280
Did he ask you to give this to me?

24:16.110 --> 24:17.230
Uncle Xu said to

24:18.310 --> 24:19.840
give him a little more time,

24:20.750 --> 24:22.480
and he will come back to see you.

24:23.630 --> 24:25.490
Let this keep you company for now.

24:28.590 --> 24:29.270
Okay.

24:31.110 --> 24:33.110
As long as he's willing to come back.

24:34.400 --> 24:35.830
I've waited for so long.

24:37.650 --> 24:39.510
I don't mind waiting a bit longer.

24:46.920 --> 24:47.920
And there's this.

25:10.440 --> 25:10.920
"Mom,

25:12.030 --> 25:13.690
rest a while if you're tired."

25:21.310 --> 25:21.750
"Mom,

25:22.910 --> 25:24.020
I miss you so much."

25:32.960 --> 25:33.440
"Mom,

25:34.110 --> 25:36.170
you must take good care of yourself."

25:47.200 --> 25:47.680
"Mom,

25:48.590 --> 25:49.990
wait for me to come home."

26:08.270 --> 26:08.680
He...

26:11.400 --> 26:11.750
He...

26:14.240 --> 26:14.590
He...

26:14.640 --> 26:15.040
Why...

26:15.350 --> 26:17.980
Why has he become like this?

26:39.640 --> 26:41.500
Mom will wait for you to come home.

26:44.790 --> 26:46.650
Mom will wait for you to come home.

27:20.670 --> 27:22.270
If I could go back in time,

27:23.790 --> 27:25.680
if I could turn back time,

27:27.680 --> 27:28.440
would everything

27:28.440 --> 27:29.640
have been different?

27:44.680 --> 27:45.550
What's wrong?

27:48.920 --> 27:50.250
Something on your mind?

27:53.000 --> 27:53.800
It's nothing.

27:55.160 --> 27:56.890
I just thought of an old friend.

28:05.110 --> 28:06.110
The hardest thing

28:07.480 --> 28:09.680
for anyone is facing themselves.

28:12.000 --> 28:13.640
Once you overcome that,

28:16.270 --> 28:17.200
nothing else in this world

28:17.200 --> 28:18.350
can stop you.

28:33.920 --> 28:34.510
Mr. Du!

28:35.300 --> 28:35.830
Mr. Du!

28:35.920 --> 28:37.720
When can we interview you?

28:44.110 --> 28:45.440
Good day, Master!

28:48.790 --> 28:49.510
Leave us.

28:50.310 --> 28:51.040
Yes, Master!

29:04.400 --> 29:05.960
Master, I can explain.

29:06.350 --> 29:07.680
It's not what you think.

29:08.240 --> 29:08.640
I...

29:09.620 --> 29:10.920
Did Zhaohui

29:11.510 --> 29:12.310
send you outside

29:12.310 --> 29:13.710
to learn to act like this?

29:15.190 --> 29:16.080
Yes, yes.

29:16.200 --> 29:17.730
It was he who had me learn it.

29:18.350 --> 29:19.790
He also asked me to seduce Zhaoji

29:19.790 --> 29:20.920
to drive a wedge between you and...

29:20.920 --> 29:21.440
Enough!

29:22.550 --> 29:23.960
How do you think I, Du Chengrong,

29:23.960 --> 29:25.400
got to where I am today?

29:26.200 --> 29:27.350
Do you think I care about

29:27.350 --> 29:28.720
those petty schemes?

29:29.750 --> 29:30.640
To me,

29:30.750 --> 29:31.310
you're just a pawn

29:31.310 --> 29:32.960
I abandoned long ago.

29:33.440 --> 29:34.440
Xia Ziyu,

29:34.680 --> 29:35.510
the affairs of my family

29:35.510 --> 29:37.040
have nothing to do with you!

29:38.310 --> 29:39.240
No, Master.

29:40.160 --> 29:41.030
I'm Vivi.

29:41.550 --> 29:42.440
I'm Vivi.

29:43.160 --> 29:43.720
Vivi.

29:45.310 --> 29:46.200
Are you the Vivi

29:46.200 --> 29:47.640
that I cherish,

29:48.640 --> 29:50.830
or the fugitive Xia Ziyu?

29:50.830 --> 29:52.400
That all depends on my mood.

29:53.240 --> 29:54.300
Do you understand?

29:56.270 --> 29:57.020
Master, I was wrong.

29:57.020 --> 29:57.750
Master, I was wrong.

29:57.750 --> 29:58.920
I'll tell you the truth.

29:58.920 --> 30:00.880
It was Zhaoji who made me pull the plug.

30:00.880 --> 30:01.880
He forced me to do it.

30:01.880 --> 30:02.480
If I hadn't done it,

30:02.480 --> 30:03.510
he would've killed me first!

30:03.510 --> 30:04.070
I was scared!

30:04.070 --> 30:05.880
He forced me, Master!

30:06.070 --> 30:07.550
So you're saying you're afraid of Zhaoji,

30:07.550 --> 30:08.680
but not afraid of me?

30:10.240 --> 30:10.640
I am.

30:10.940 --> 30:11.720
I am afraid.

30:11.960 --> 30:12.240
I...

30:12.260 --> 30:13.900
I stayed by your side at the hospital
for two days.

30:13.900 --> 30:14.880
I thought you really

30:14.880 --> 30:15.960
wouldn't wake up.

30:16.110 --> 30:18.240
That's why I listened to his nonsense.

30:19.350 --> 30:21.920
Zhaohui sent you to me,

30:22.350 --> 30:23.880
so I accepted that gesture

30:24.350 --> 30:26.350
and kept you around for amusement.

30:26.790 --> 30:28.250
Whatever you were before,

30:28.720 --> 30:30.120
or whatever you've done—

30:30.160 --> 30:31.640
none of that matters to me.

30:32.510 --> 30:33.060
Master...

30:33.060 --> 30:34.660
I gave you wealth and status,

30:35.640 --> 30:37.440
and you got to show off in public.

30:38.590 --> 30:39.790
Did you really think

30:40.160 --> 30:41.680
that I trusted your abilities,

30:41.680 --> 30:42.720
or that

30:42.720 --> 30:44.720
I only favored you?

30:45.090 --> 30:45.550
Master,

30:45.550 --> 30:47.160
I don't want anything anymore.

30:47.160 --> 30:48.440
I don't want anything anymore, Master!

30:48.440 --> 30:50.200
I just want to stay by your side,

30:50.200 --> 30:50.660
Master!

30:50.880 --> 30:52.450
Please spare me this once!

30:52.480 --> 30:53.830
Spare me this once!

30:53.850 --> 30:55.480
Forgive you? Spare you?

30:55.590 --> 30:57.250
How am I supposed to spare you?

30:57.440 --> 30:59.370
Which one do you want me to forgive?

31:00.070 --> 31:02.070
The time
you and Zhaohui conspired to trick me,

31:02.070 --> 31:04.350
or the time you and Zhaoji conspired

31:04.350 --> 31:05.880
to kill me?

31:08.830 --> 31:10.350
I don't think you should stay here.

31:10.350 --> 31:11.400
You should go back

31:11.400 --> 31:12.530
to where you belong.

31:13.190 --> 31:13.760
No...

31:14.240 --> 31:14.680
No.

31:14.790 --> 31:15.790
I don't want to go back!

31:15.790 --> 31:16.750
I don't want to go back, Master!

31:16.750 --> 31:17.510
I'll be good!

31:17.510 --> 31:18.640
Master, I was wrong!

31:23.640 --> 31:24.110
What?

31:24.830 --> 31:25.350
Scared?

31:26.510 --> 31:28.150
Scared that I'll send you away, right?

31:28.150 --> 31:28.880
No, no.

31:28.960 --> 31:29.720
No, I don't want to.

31:29.720 --> 31:31.000
No, I'm not going back!

31:31.160 --> 31:32.430
I don't want to go back, Master!

31:32.430 --> 31:34.240
I don't want to go back, Master!

31:34.960 --> 31:36.760
You've always relied on others.

31:37.110 --> 31:38.400
This time, whether you live or die

31:38.400 --> 31:39.380
depends on you.

31:41.000 --> 31:41.920
Du Zhaoji

31:42.070 --> 31:43.480
has a forged will.

31:44.160 --> 31:45.110
Go get it for me.

31:48.880 --> 31:49.750
You should know

31:50.390 --> 31:51.390
where he keeps it.

31:53.790 --> 31:54.790
Don't let me down.

32:23.880 --> 32:25.080
Everything's ready?

32:27.720 --> 32:29.400
Du Chengrong has insisted on
sending someone

32:29.400 --> 32:30.400
to follow Xia Ziyu

32:30.720 --> 32:32.510
to ensure she doesn't run away midway.

32:32.510 --> 32:33.550
That actually

32:33.680 --> 32:34.820
works in our favor.

32:36.680 --> 32:37.980
Du Chengrong is probably thinking that

32:37.980 --> 32:39.280
if your plan fails,

32:39.640 --> 32:40.680
he'll deal with Xia Ziyu

32:40.680 --> 32:41.550
in his own way.

32:42.110 --> 32:43.240
He won't let this go.

32:43.680 --> 32:45.240
He won't make life easy for Xia Ziyu.

32:45.240 --> 32:47.030
Tell me, for Xia Ziyu,

32:48.000 --> 32:49.270
which is worse:

32:49.510 --> 32:50.880
being dealt with by Du Chengrong

32:50.880 --> 32:52.280
or being dealt with by me?

32:52.720 --> 32:54.920
If she falls into Du Chengrong's hands,

32:55.110 --> 32:57.510
she might be thrown back
to the Walled City.

32:57.720 --> 32:59.320
If she falls into your hands,

32:59.790 --> 33:01.390
she has to face her past self.

33:01.640 --> 33:02.830
I just want her to face

33:02.830 --> 33:05.160
everything she's been running away from.

33:09.960 --> 33:10.790
Going out?

33:12.480 --> 33:13.440
Come back early.

33:14.030 --> 33:16.860
I managed to buy a free-range chicken
from the countryside.

33:16.860 --> 33:17.270
Okay.

33:17.720 --> 33:19.320
We'll try to come back early.

33:19.480 --> 33:19.960
Okay.

33:20.400 --> 33:21.660
Call your mom over too.

33:21.960 --> 33:23.560
The soup she makes is better.

33:24.030 --> 33:24.440
Okay.

33:24.890 --> 33:25.550
We're heading out now.

33:25.550 --> 33:25.960
Okay.

33:26.240 --> 33:27.010
Bye, Granny Yu.

33:27.010 --> 33:27.870
Bye, Granny Yu.

33:52.070 --> 33:53.480
You will never beat me.

34:24.949 --> 34:26.199
Ms. Vivi, please.

34:40.960 --> 34:41.880
Hello, Mom.

34:42.510 --> 34:43.880
Ge Jian will pick you up in a while

34:43.880 --> 34:45.150
to go to Granny Yu's house.

34:45.150 --> 34:46.710
Zhenzhu will go there too.

34:46.920 --> 34:48.760
She wants to talk to you about Luna.

34:48.760 --> 34:49.190
Okay.

34:49.840 --> 34:51.710
Tonight I want to have the soup you make.

34:51.710 --> 34:53.040
Wait for me there, okay?

34:53.550 --> 34:54.000
Okay.

34:55.840 --> 34:56.280
Bye.

34:59.550 --> 35:00.550
Was that Xiaolan?

35:01.630 --> 35:03.360
She said she wants chicken soup

35:03.590 --> 35:06.230
and asked me to go to Granny Yu's
to make it for her.

35:06.230 --> 35:07.280
Since she arranged it,

35:07.280 --> 35:08.540
just go along with her.

35:10.810 --> 35:11.710
Then, after you get off work,

35:11.710 --> 35:12.440
come join us?

35:12.960 --> 35:13.490
Alright.

35:15.360 --> 35:16.090
Is that okay?

35:16.480 --> 35:17.340
More than okay.

35:20.760 --> 35:21.280
Go.

35:21.960 --> 35:23.090
The goodbye ritual.

35:25.160 --> 35:27.680
Don't talk to strangers outside.

35:27.710 --> 35:29.510
Don't accept candy from anyone.

35:29.800 --> 35:30.590
This ritual?

35:33.760 --> 35:34.720
Alright, alright, alright.

35:34.720 --> 35:35.280
See you tonight.

35:35.280 --> 35:36.210
See you tonight.

35:40.360 --> 35:41.960
Du Zhaoji has been arrested.

35:42.190 --> 35:44.280
Xia Ziyu is coming to Shengcheng alone.

35:44.280 --> 35:46.680
Aren't you worried she might have helpers?

35:46.840 --> 35:47.590
I don't know.

35:48.630 --> 35:49.490
On Kong Island,

35:50.070 --> 35:53.000
there were plenty of women
trying to get close to Du Chengrong.

35:53.000 --> 35:54.480
The fact that Xia Ziyu pulled it off

35:54.480 --> 35:56.070
means she's got both cunning

35:56.070 --> 35:56.840
and brains.

35:57.400 --> 35:58.800
With Du Zhaoji arrested,

35:58.880 --> 35:59.590
there are quite a few people

35:59.590 --> 36:01.250
left stranded in his network.

36:01.440 --> 36:02.840
Who knows—

36:03.190 --> 36:04.440
someone with nothing left to lose

36:04.440 --> 36:05.190
might throw in with Xia Ziyu

36:05.190 --> 36:06.320
for one last gamble.

36:21.440 --> 36:22.200
No! Go away!

36:21.530 --> 36:23.680
[Shengcheng]

36:22.230 --> 36:22.830
Thank you.

36:22.830 --> 36:23.490
No! Go away!

36:24.060 --> 36:24.880
Thank you.

36:33.550 --> 36:34.190
Thank you.

36:34.880 --> 36:36.880
Spare some change for food, please?

36:38.440 --> 36:39.840
Please spare some change for food.

36:39.840 --> 36:40.630
Please spare some change for food.

36:40.630 --> 36:41.560
I lost this hand.

36:41.630 --> 36:42.210
I lost this hand.

36:42.210 --> 36:44.270
Please s-spare some change for food.

36:45.900 --> 36:47.310
[Thank you, kind soul.
Please have pity on me.]

36:47.210 --> 36:48.940
Ziyu, you got into university?

36:49.550 --> 36:51.410
My daughter got into university.

36:52.150 --> 36:53.350
You're our village's

36:53.480 --> 36:55.010
first university student.

37:10.440 --> 37:12.370
Please spare some change for food.

37:16.440 --> 37:17.040
Thank you.

37:17.480 --> 37:18.070
Thank you.

37:18.070 --> 37:18.530
Go away!

37:18.760 --> 37:19.710
Go away!

37:42.150 --> 37:44.960
Freshly roasted sweet potatoes!

37:45.550 --> 37:46.550
Auntie,

37:46.770 --> 37:47.450
I'm hungry.

37:47.480 --> 37:48.800
Can you buy me

37:48.800 --> 37:49.840
a roasted sweet potato?

37:49.840 --> 37:50.840
I'll give you the money,
and you go buy it yourself,

37:50.840 --> 37:51.230
okay?

37:51.710 --> 37:54.320
It's right there.
I want you to buy one for me.

37:54.440 --> 37:55.400
Alright. Wait here.

37:55.400 --> 37:56.660
I'll go buy one for you.

37:58.410 --> 37:59.670
Roasted sweet potatoes!

37:59.670 --> 38:02.320
Delicious, hot roasted sweet potatoes!

38:03.000 --> 38:04.360
Roasted sweet potatoes!

38:04.360 --> 38:06.920
Delicious, hot roasted sweet potatoes!

38:09.900 --> 38:10.530
Ziyu...

38:13.800 --> 38:14.930
This is real, right?

38:15.840 --> 38:17.480
I'm so happy for you.

38:18.480 --> 38:19.590
I'm so proud of you.

38:22.250 --> 38:23.730
Roasted sweet potatoes!

38:23.760 --> 38:26.360
Delicious, hot roasted sweet potatoes!

38:27.280 --> 38:28.680
Roasted sweet potatoes!

38:28.960 --> 38:30.490
Get a roasted sweet potato!

38:48.100 --> 38:49.480
Roasted sweet potatoes!

38:49.480 --> 38:51.530
Roasted sweet potatoes! Wanna try a piece?

38:51.530 --> 38:52.920
Roasted sweet potatoes!

38:52.920 --> 38:54.960
Freshly roasted sweet potatoes!

38:55.230 --> 38:56.760
Miss, freshly roasted sweet potatoes!

38:56.760 --> 38:57.510
Want one?

38:57.760 --> 38:58.760
They're so sweet!

38:59.440 --> 39:00.440
Try a piece?

39:00.440 --> 39:01.440
Freshly roasted!

39:01.590 --> 39:02.150
No, thanks.

39:02.150 --> 39:03.070
They're very sweet!

39:03.070 --> 39:03.550
No, thanks.

39:03.550 --> 39:05.230
Have a piece! Freshly roasted!

39:05.230 --> 39:05.890
No, thanks.

39:07.550 --> 39:09.210
Freshly roasted! Very sweet!

39:15.760 --> 39:17.290
This is only the beginning.

39:17.920 --> 39:18.710
Xia Ziyu.

39:32.470 --> 39:33.980
Z-Ziyu?

39:35.800 --> 39:36.800
Is that you, Ziyu?

39:37.230 --> 39:39.090
I heard you were on Kong Island...

39:47.760 --> 39:49.180
[Shengcheng Commercial Bank]

40:06.000 --> 40:06.800
Ms. Vivi,

40:06.960 --> 40:08.840
this is safe deposit box No. 237.

40:10.760 --> 40:11.630
I'll wait outside.

40:11.630 --> 40:13.070
Call me if you need anything.

40:13.070 --> 40:13.670
Thank you.

40:43.240 --> 40:45.230
[To: Xia Xiaolan]

41:12.070 --> 41:12.600
Jianhua,

41:13.190 --> 41:14.230
this is our Dahe Village's

41:14.230 --> 41:15.430
rice field this year.

41:15.710 --> 41:16.760
Growing quite well.

41:16.760 --> 41:17.800
Looks like the harvest this year

41:17.800 --> 41:18.660
should be good.

41:19.230 --> 41:19.590
Yes.

41:19.670 --> 41:21.130
The grains are quite full.

41:22.220 --> 41:22.710
Ziyu.

41:22.760 --> 41:23.230
What?

41:24.110 --> 41:25.110
Isn't that Wang Jianhua—

41:25.110 --> 41:26.110
the new agricultural technician

41:26.110 --> 41:27.710
who just came to our village?

41:28.070 --> 41:30.150
We should... still layer the rice.

41:30.360 --> 41:31.120
Each layer

41:31.150 --> 41:32.880
contains rice at various stages of growth.

41:32.880 --> 41:34.210
City folk are city folk.

41:34.510 --> 41:35.630
Even after being here for so long,

41:35.630 --> 41:36.480
he's still not quite the same

41:36.480 --> 41:37.410
as us villagers.

41:39.630 --> 41:40.630
Hello, everyone!

41:40.800 --> 41:43.400
Working hard under this hot sun—
that's tough!

41:43.510 --> 41:44.230
Not at all.

41:44.400 --> 41:45.000
Not at all.

41:45.110 --> 41:45.640
Jianhua,

41:45.840 --> 41:46.880
let's go check over there.

41:46.880 --> 41:47.230
Okay.

41:47.880 --> 41:49.590
The timing of each season is also crucial.

41:49.590 --> 41:50.110
Well...

41:50.670 --> 41:52.230
When will he go back to the city?

41:52.230 --> 41:53.000
Who knows?

41:53.480 --> 41:54.840
Maybe after staying here for a long time,

41:54.840 --> 41:55.470
he wouldn't want to leave.

41:55.470 --> 41:56.880
It wouldn't be bad
if he married a wife here and stayed.

41:56.880 --> 41:57.480
Marry who?

41:57.550 --> 41:58.190
You?

41:58.840 --> 41:59.510
He's from the city.

41:59.510 --> 42:00.770
He has high standards.

42:00.880 --> 42:02.320
He probably wouldn't fancy
a village girl like us.

42:02.320 --> 42:03.800
That's not necessarily true.

42:03.800 --> 42:05.530
Come on, let's get back to work.

42:12.360 --> 42:13.120
Jianhua.

42:13.320 --> 42:14.650
Xiaolan, why did you...

42:15.760 --> 42:16.090
Zi...

42:16.670 --> 42:17.670
Zi... Ziyu?

42:18.230 --> 42:19.830
Do... do you need something?

42:31.510 --> 42:34.190
This is a love letter for Xiaolan?

42:34.940 --> 42:35.960
No, it's not.

42:38.000 --> 42:38.410
Ziyu,

42:38.440 --> 42:40.570
did you just say you needed something?

42:43.670 --> 42:44.320
Jianhua,

42:45.280 --> 42:47.140
actually, I've always liked you.

43:09.150 --> 43:10.630
I mean every word.

43:10.920 --> 43:12.580
I've liked you for a long time.

43:50.670 --> 43:51.330
Movie time!

43:51.380 --> 43:52.310
It's movie time.

43:59.660 --> 44:00.870
Xia Ziyu

44:01.150 --> 44:03.280
has always been exceptionally proud.

44:03.840 --> 44:05.440
Relying on her little tricks,

44:05.440 --> 44:08.040
she'd monopolized
Grandma Xia's affections.

44:08.150 --> 44:09.670
She naturally assumed

44:09.960 --> 44:11.320
that all the best things

44:11.840 --> 44:12.880
should be hers.

44:13.920 --> 44:15.180
But she never expected

44:15.590 --> 44:17.320
that the one she had always dismissed—

44:17.320 --> 44:19.380
the seemingly carefree Xia Xiaolan—

44:20.360 --> 44:22.090
would win Wang Jianhua's heart

44:22.280 --> 44:23.590
before she could.

44:25.190 --> 44:25.960
Of course, Xia Ziyu

44:25.960 --> 44:27.290
liked Wang Jianhua too.

44:29.110 --> 44:30.550
But the moment she saw

44:30.550 --> 44:31.550
that love letter,

44:33.000 --> 44:34.150
what she wanted more

44:35.000 --> 44:37.530
was the thrill
of stealing Wang Jianhua away.

45:01.710 --> 45:02.670
It really is you.
